	   <tr><td colspan=2>These items fall under the Trivial Loot Code rules on the Firiona Vie server.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you are on this server, get a group together, and pull these before you get too high level.<br>I'd recommend a highlevel druid Tracking them for you, but just be sure the druid is not in the party when combat begins, or the hearts won't drop. I learned this the hard way, after reaching level 24 Druid status, i figured they'd be easy to get, and I could avoid them accursed brownies.  Wrong on both accounts... :(<br><br>Vae Ventus Fatum<br>Druidess - Firiona Vie Server<br>&nbsp;<br>Keety<br>Vah Shir Shaman - Firion Vie</td></tr>
