	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;Just to try to help with drop rate when i started this quest i was using a crustation shield which has negitive charisma, killed 16 with no hearts droped, when to sell loot and have charisma items in inventory to get better money, changed when i sold and forgot to change them when i went back and first ghast i killed there was a heart, kept charisma items on and next 3 kills 3 hearts, seems like the higher your charisma the better chance of there being a heart, to help everyone out, good luck, worth the time!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
