	   <tr><td colspan=2>I killed 10 Ghasts to get my 4 hearts. It took me about 4 hours to get them all. But I had the advantage of Wolf Form and Track. So while getting the hearts was easy for me, I don't know how easy it would be for someone without those two skills. <br><br>I found killing the roaming skeletons did make the Ghasts spawn, but only at night. REALLY watch out for Equesterella the Corupt.....She WILL kill you if you are anywhere near her!! I managed to out run here in Wolf Form an few times, but she hit me for 401 points of damage each time!! So watch out for her, she is a black colored horse I believe.......I ran away so fast I didn't get a good look at her :-) Happy Hunting!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
